column2: SELECT C.objID, C.z, A.zphot, B.distance, A.SFR_UV, D.ssfr, A.logMstar, D.logMass FROM MyDB.CCOSEDProps as A CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (A.RAJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER, A.DEJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER, #/#.) AS B JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS C ON B.objID = C.objID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as D on C.specObjID = D.specObjID INTO MyDB.CCOSEDProps_SpecPhotoAllFGED
